                <div class="arrow arrow-1">1. Jądro (protoni + neutrony)</div>
                <div class="arrow arrow-2">2. Protony (ładunek +)</div>
                <div class="arrow arrow-3">3. Neutrony (bez ładunku)</div>
                <div class="arrow arrow-4">4. Elektrony (ładunek -)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="water-schema">
                <div class="atom-h"></div>
